    <stitle>5 SPEED AND 6 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - REMOVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>REMOVE</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
            <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER</title>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Remote control housings are removed the same way as gear shift levers.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the four (4) retaining bolts from the gear shift lever base (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1302604">Figure 4</hotlnk>).
                </para>
                <figure id="f1302604" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="g1302604" filename="../figg13/G1302604.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                    <caption>Figure 4. Remove Retaining Bolts From Gear Shift Lever Base, Break Gasket Seal and Remove
                        Gear Shift Lever Housing
                    </caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">To break the gasket seal, lightly jar the gear shift housing (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1302604">Figure 4</hotlnk>).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the gear shift lever housing (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f1302604">Figure 4</hotlnk>).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the gasket and clean all mounting surfaces of gasket material.</para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
